Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.51,0:01:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I know how to get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides I've known about you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the project!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:52.13,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06303B&\fs72.605\pos(731.685,134.621)}Project
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To Tatsuhiro Sato,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have been chosen for my project.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Therefore please come to Mita Park on 4th Street at 9:00 tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Misaki Nakahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A contract regarding how to escape the hikikomori state and recovery support...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's handwritten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, the penalty charge is one hundred thousand yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you really okay with hanging out with a weirdo like me this late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:44.81,Note,,0,0,0,,Beware of Molesters\NCall 119 if you spot suspicious activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So Sato, were you the guilty party?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides my house is right around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a part of soliciting too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, about yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just tagging along with my Aunt Kazuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've caused all kinds of problems for my aunt for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so that was the least I could do for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, go ahead and sign the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna know how to escape being a hikikomori, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how, once you sign the contract, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me like I'm your friend! You're younger than me! Show some respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how old I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... I'd guess around 17 or 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, you're correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, you're going to regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be your last chance, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you at the same time tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign this and bring it back. All right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:18.15,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs42.352}Contract Re: How to Escape the Hikikomori State and Recovery Support\NHikikomori Subject: Tatsuhiro Sato\NRecovery Supporter: Misaki Nakahara
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki Nakahara...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll bring you today's show with our lovely guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Afternoon Time! I'm your host Sewashi Sekiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And today's guests are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Another day is coming to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a day void of any significant events.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How long am I going to repeat days like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, I read a sci-fi novel like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The story takes place in the near future, after the human race is annihilated in the final war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The main character is the only survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain life forms from outer space, to put it simply, aliens,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,decide to keep this main character alive as a test sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So they create a simulation of Earth as it had been,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to hide the truth that mankind had been wiped out from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if he were to spend too much time outside of his house,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,he would figure out that the world he lives in is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So they decide to make the main character a NEET so they can isolate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The main character, me, Tatsuhiro Sato,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,kept alive as part of a horrifying alien conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dreams and hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Magical girl, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:07:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This contract is made by and between the person who suffers from hikikomorism, hereinafter "subject"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the person who helps him/her recover from the condition, hereinafter "supporter". {number 9 is the supporter}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Both parties agree to the terms as follows:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,1) The Subject must disclose all feelings, including but not limited to:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Distress, conflict, complaints, negative thoughts, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding hikikomori recovery procedures to the Supporter. {inb4 Juiz}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Signing this damned paper would fix my hikikomori condition? Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting for you at the same time tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That chick is totally clueless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of hikikomori would go outside two days in a row anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're called "hikikomori" because we don't go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This could be your last chance, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it really was my last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But now the chance is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Could she be still waiting for me out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:21.64,Note,,0,0,0,,Beware of Molesters\NCall 119 if you spot suspicious activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! That park is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:58.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\pos(640,33.278)}Misaki Nakahara Emergency Press Conference
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to meet my friend there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but he didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept on waiting and waiting, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your friend's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of relationship do you have with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sato, can we talk to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We know you're in there! Please come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your hikikomori condition, an innocent young girl has been deeply scarred!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to apologize to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.68,Note,,0,0,0,,Beware of Molesters\NCall 119 if you spot suspicious activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're an hour late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You... What the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:10:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a sweet little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,who's willing to rescue a hikikomori loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not a hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite obvious when my aunt and I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I told you guys that I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But normally people wouldn't get flustered like that unless they are hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring the contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not a hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You come to this park every Sunday night and do nothing but gaze into space, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But other than that, you don't go outside at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, that's a hikikomori condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's... it's true that I'm always in my apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't help it because of my work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,SOHO...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,SOHO?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It means "small office home office"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I'm working from home, so it's not like I'm unemployed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you came to the coffee shop for a job interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just did that on a whim! That was an impulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of job do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, don't be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a creator!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Since my job requires me to be creative, I may come off sort of weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's just an aspect of my brilliant talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you create?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the most advanced, revolutionary IT...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! It's computer-related!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Software development, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm in the middle of making software! It's so awesome it'd put even Bill or Linus to shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to bring the contract tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bring it tomorrow," my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare she look at me like she's some kind of know-it-all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I could easily write a program or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to put up with this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come out, I'll break it down myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn that shit down! Turn off that goddamn animu song!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Sato, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real? Are you real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the anime otaku who moved in next door,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:25.28,Note,,0,0,0,,Literature Club
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Join the Literature Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Those few words made me decide to spend my three high school years in the Literature Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I had no interest in novels whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my daily club activities were playing cards and hanging out with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,listening to her bizarre conspiracy theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, what the hell was I doing back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there were lots of other things I could have been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years rolled by very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And one day, shortly before her graduation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's bullying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I go help the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, they're just middle school kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullying is not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly the hunter became the hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She was amazed how pathetic I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but supposedly the guy being bullied was deeply moved by my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.36,Note,,0,0,0,,Literature Club
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to join the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Four years after my graduation, this is an unexpected reunion indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it's messy. Please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought the anime song freak next door was Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the walls of this apartment are pretty thin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Usually, people would realize stuff like that a few days after they moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've been listening to it every single day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I've become numb to the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize you live right next door to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but I always knew that you'd go to college in Tokyo though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your fourth year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been going to a vocational school in Tokyo since this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for an apartment that's easy to commute from and cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I found this place and I liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was already predicting that he'd probably end up like this four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, have you been bullied at the school you go to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You were crying earlier, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People in my class are nothing but morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know a thing about video games!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But they all act like they know what they're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanna ask them why they even bother coming to the school at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, there's no hope for the future of Japan's video game industry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Up we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, it was so much fun back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish those carefree days had never ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.35,Note,,0,0,0,,Game Creator Department\NKokogi Designer Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Designer Institute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, haven't you seen the TV commercial before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've been going to the Game Creator Department of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.77,Note,,0,0,0,,Game Creator Department\NKokogi Designer Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Game Creator Department...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a creator!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki, can I borrow this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:50.00,Note,,0,0,0,,Beware of Molesters\NCall 119 if you spot suspicious activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right on time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring the contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What I told you last night wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I graduated from the Game Creator Department of a design institute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This book looks like it's brand new.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have to read things once to get the general idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been that way all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What does "object-oriented" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, now you understand that I'm a creator, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then will you show it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The game you've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:32.42,Note,,0,0,0,,Beware of Molesters\NCall 119 if you spot suspicious activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, it's not finished yet, and I'm not supposed to show it to the general public.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your graduation project would do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just junk that I made before I became a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So anything but that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You are very gifted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If... If you insist, fine, I'll show it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My masterpiece from the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But not right away though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even remember where I put it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, I'm busy with some of my most important work right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd probably be sometime next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next month then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yamazaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a college-dropout and have been a hikikomori for the last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought that you're a NEET?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, you told such a huge lie just to impress a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It kinda slipped out on the spur of the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, Yamazaki, I have a little favor to ask of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're thinking about asking me to lend you a game I've made, forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just started classes at that school myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything that's decent enough to let you borrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try to make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just to show off for some girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:20:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you succeed, you might be able to recover from being a NEET!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And gaining experience is beneficial for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to make a game together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, what kind of skills do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, can you draw, or make music or program?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm totally hopeless when it comes to stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that means scripting the scenario is about the only think you could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Scenario?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the scriptwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hell no, I haven't "composed" anything since I was in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were in the Literature Club, weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about this. Have you ever read any novel written by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all writing stuff is a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna do this or not?! Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he's a wuss, he can be short-tempered and very argumentative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he was bullied to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be able to come up with something for the scenario!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the problem is time, since you promised her that you were going to show it to her next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we had a little bit more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is making a game such a big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to a big project, it usually takes a few of years to produce it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,a several hundred people to work on it and hundreds of billion yen to fund it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are people out there with no money or help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't even program anything decent, and all they have is some crappy music.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,However, even if one's situation is that miserable,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a certain game genre that still allows you to produce a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you're lucky, get rich quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome, Yamazaki! That is it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But this road will be difficult and painted in our sweat and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell me, "You know what? I quit!" In the middle of production!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is the game genre you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Erotic game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HD19526&\pos(640,136.135)\fs60.504}Episode 02
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(656.18,468.907)\fs60.504\c&HCF8900&}Welcome to the Creator!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:21:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The ocean of the Internet is my ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite honestly, I don't think it's normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.38,0:23:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the world, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode, "Welcome to the Beautiful Girls!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,113.445)\fs60.504\c&H88D447&}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,446.219)\fs60.504\c&H77BE35&}Welcome to the Beautiful Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.18,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.26,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.31,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,as I turn my back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:24.64,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:27.81,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,"Where am I supposed to go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:32.86,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:42.20,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,In the shadows of a back alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:49.33,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the hands of a clock repaint the time that has been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.07,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Extended hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:57.44,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,puzzle pieces that don't fit.
